dhcp leases list
================
/var/lib/dnsmasq/dnsmasq.leases
/var/lib/misc/dnsmasq.leases
grep 00:25:90:fe:f8:68 /var/lib/misc/dnsmasq.leases

MAC=
grep $MAC /var/lib/misc/dnsmasq.leases; grep $MAC /var/log/messages


error messages from syslog
==========================
tail -f /var/log/messages | grep -v "available DHCP range\|vendor class\|client provides\|56:00\|52:54"

tcpdump -i eth0 -n port bootpc or port bootps -vvv

